    <title>Hexo创建github博客</title>
    <url>/2021/08/19/blog/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h4 id="搭建博客"><a href="#搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客"></a>搭建博客</h4><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n/">相关借鉴视频</a>：<a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n/">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n/</a></p>
<div style="font-size:0.75em">
    <div style="text-indent:2em">我是Zhenyue，zhen-yue.github.io这一网站的持有者，谨代表本站欢迎你的莅临。</div><br>
    <div style="text-indent:2em">我通过该网站记录自己的学习足迹，同时分享自己学到的知识和想法，愿与诸位共同进步。感谢 GitHub 的技术支持，本博客网站因此能够建立，并拥有一个属于自己的独立域名。通过 GitHub 建立静态博客，不仅降低了运营的成本，且不用花费额外的精力去维护服务器。</div><br>
    <div style="text-indent:2em">该博客采用 Hexo 框架，主题为 Next，源码存放于 GitHub，通过 Git 进行部署。该博客同时适配移动端和PC端浏览器，方便随时随地进行浏览。</div><br>
    <div style="text-indent:2em">著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。本文为Zhenyue原创，依据<a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/">CC BY-NC-SA 4.0</a>许可证进行授权，转载请附上出处链接及本声明。</div><br>
    <div style="text-indent:2em">如果你在浏览博客的过程中发现任何问题，欢迎前往 GitHub 的代码仓库提交 Issues 。如果你有其他事情想要咨询，可以通过邮件联系我，邮箱地址：zhen_yue@foxmail.com。</div>
    <br>
</div>

<figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ git --version</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ node -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ npm -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)     </span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)   </span><br><span class="line">#全部回车略过，C:\Users\Administrator\.ssh、id_rsa.pub找到ssh Keys复制到github</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master) </span><br><span class="line">#测试ssh绑定是否成功</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#初始化</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#本地部署server</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#安装自动部署发布工具</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#清除public缓存</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#生成generate页面</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64  ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#上传到github部署，需要用户名和密码，注意密码是github的Personal access tokens</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#hexo g -d即可同时完成hexo g和hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<h4 id="问题解决"><a href="#问题解决" class="headerlink" title="问题解决"></a>问题解决</h4><figure class="highlight cmd"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP  MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#补全环境</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#错误：Something&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can <span class="built_in">find</span> the solution here: %s https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span><br><span class="line">#常因网络速度过慢出现的问题，重试即可</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#错误：(node:<span class="number">4396</span>) ExperimentalWarning: The <span class="built_in">fs</span>.promises API is experimental</span><br><span class="line">Administrator@DESKTOP MINGW64 ~/Desktop/blog (master)</span><br><span class="line">#通过nvm下载最新版node</span><br><span class="line">$ nvm install latest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">##部分相关命令</span><br><span class="line">#启用nvm</span><br><span class="line">$ nvm on</span><br><span class="line">#展示所有版本</span><br><span class="line">$ nvm ls</span><br><span class="line">#选择node版本</span><br><span class="line">$ nvm use <span class="number">19</span>.<span class="number">6</span>.<span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

